.Dt UVIDEO 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm uvideo
.Nd USB video devices
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "uvideo*     at uhub?"
.Cd "video*      at uvideo?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver supports a range of USB Video Class (UVC) devices including webcams,
camcorders and other cameras.
UVC is a generic specification and many USB video devices follow it.
